descriptionHtml:
Salfeld’s Child Control can provide safe filtered Internet with parental control features, once you activate the app with your account details from Salfeld. Child Control runs both on Android phones and tablets and filtering can be tuned from any PC with any OS connected to the Internet.

Salfeld’s Child Control can provide safe filtered Internet with parental control features, once you activate the app with your account details from Salfeld. Child Control runs both on Android phones and tablets and filtering can be tuned from any PC with any OS connected to the Internet.

This app uses the Device Administrator permission. This will prevent a user from uninstalling Salfeld Child Control App without your knowledge.

Salfeld Child Control uses AccessibilityService API to collect data about websites viewed through browsers on your child's device. It is also used to prevent the child from removing permissions without a parent’s authentication.

Salfeld’s Child Control can provide safe filtered Internet with parental control features, once you activate the app with your account details from Salfeld. Child Control runs both on Android phones and tablets and filtering can be tuned from any PC with any OS connected to the Internet.

The App can be used up to 30 days for free. After this period a licence is needed. See our homepage for more information.

Important notes:
This app uses the Device Administrator permission. This will prevent a user from uninstalling Salfeld Child Control App without your knowledge.

Salfeld Child Control uses AccessibilityService API to collect data about websites viewed through browsers on your child's device. It is also used to prevent the child from removing permissions without a parent’s authentication.
descriptionShort: Safe and time limited mobile experience for kids and teens
